OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson reveals 'aggressive'
OL,4,Ccancer diagnosis
OL,6,FJeremy Clarkson has revealed he has
OL,7,Fbeen diagnosed with an "aggressive"
OL,8,Fform of cancer during filming of the
OL,9,Ffifth series of his documentary series
OL,10,FClarkson's Farm.
OL,12,FOn the show, Clarkson, 66, is seen
OL,13,Ftelling visibly shocked co-stars Kaleb
OL,14,FCooper and Charlie Ireland the news.
OL,16,FThe former Top Gear presenter did not
OL,17,Freveal what form of cancer he had been
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with, but he did say it had
OL,19,Fbeen caught early.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
