OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781707674
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson reveals 'aggressive'
OL,4,Ccancer diagnosis
OL,6,FThe TV presenter went on to say: "I
OL,7,Fwas praying we could get the harvest
OL,8,Fdone and then I could go and get some
OL,9,Ftreatment, but it's going to be slap
OL,10,Fbang in the middle."
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHe told them he had known "since May",
OL,18,Falthough it is not clear what year
OL,19,Fthis was.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781707674
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson reveals 'aggressive'
OL,4,Ccancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"I disappeared off the other week and
OL,7,FI had a biopsy, and it is cancer, and
OL,8,Fit's aggressive, but it's really
OL,9,Fearly", he said.
OL,11,F"I promise I'll be fine," he told the
OL,12,Ftwo men, adding that he would be out
OL,13,Fof action "for a little while".
OL,15,FLater in the episode, he was seen in a
OL,16,Fhospital bed waiting for surgery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
