PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781707674
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson reveals 'aggressive'
OL,4,Ccancer diagnosis
OL,6,FSeveral hours before the release of
OL,7,Fthe final two episodes, Clarkson
OL,8,Fposted an Instagram video warning fans
OL,9,Fthat they would be a "really, really
OL,10,Fdifficult watch".
OL,12,FThe fifth series of the Amazon Prime
OL,13,Fshow began filming in 2024 at his
OL,14,FDiddly Squat Farm in Oxfordshire.
OL,16,FClarkson revealed in his column in The
OL,17,FSunday Times that he had a stent
OL,18,Ffitted at John Radcliffe Hospital in
OL,19,FOxford after experiencing a "sudden
OL,20,Fdeterioration" in his health after
OL,21,Freturning from holiday in October 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
